			</p>
			<a
				href="/uses"
				class="inline-block rounded-md bg-teal px-4 py-2 font-medium text-surface-0 no-underline hover:bg-coral"
			>
				See my uses &rarr;
			</a>
		</div>

		<!-- Work History - git log styled timeline -->
		<h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">
			<span class="text-coral font-mono text-sm" aria-hidden="true">~$</span> git log --oneline --graph
			career/
		</h2>
		<div class="mb-10 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
			<!-- CloudQuery - current -->
			<details class="group">
				<summary
					class="cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-surface-1 rounded px-2 py-1 transition-colors"
				>
					<span class="text-coral font-bold">*</span>
					<span class="text-amber-400">90e3919</span>
					<span class="text-teal">(HEAD -&gt; main)</span>
					<span class="font-bold text-white">Developer Advocate - CloudQuery</span>
					<span class="text-gray-400">(2025-present)</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="ml-4 border-l border-gray-600 pl-4 pb-2">
					<pre
						class="text-gray-400 whitespace-pre-wrap text-xs mt-1 bg-surface-1 rounded p-3"><span class="text-amber-400">commit 90e3919</span>
<span class="text-white">Author:</span> Joe Karlsson &lt;joe@karlsson.com&gt;
<span class="text-white">Date:</span>   2025

    <span class="text-white font-bold">Developer Advocate - CloudQuery</span>

    Developer relations and content for the open-source ELT framework.
    Creating demos, tutorials, and developer resources for data pipelines.</pre>
				</div>
			</details>
			<div class="text-gray-600 pl-2">
				|&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="text-gray-400"
					>Developer relations and content for the open-source ELT framework.</span>
			</div>
			<div class="text-gray-600 pl-2">|</div>

			<!-- Tinybird -->
			<details class="group">
