						intersection of art and computer science, and previously built developer communities at
						MongoDB, SingleStore, and Tinybird. Before DevRel, he was a Front-end Technical Lead at
						Best Buy and a Full-Stack JavaScript instructor. Outside of work, he runs a 40+
						container homelab, automates his home with Home Assistant, and once built an
						IoT-connected cat litter box that he gave a conference talk about.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
